Laazmi hai ke tum mujhse parda karo
Apni shaadi ke din ab nahin door hai
Main bhi tadpa karoon, tum bhi tadpa karo
Badi mushkil hai, yeh mera dil hai
Tum hi kaho kaise main chup rahoon
